<h3>Past PhD students</h3>

<p>I have supervised the following PhDs at Birmingham:</p>
<ul>

<li>Asiri Rathnayake, graduated in 2015, now Compiler Engineer at  ARM Ltd in Cambridge. Thesis title: Semantics, Analysis and Security of Backtracking Regular Expression Matchers</li>

<li>Maxim Strygin, graduated 2014, now at HP in Moscow. Thesis title: Semantics and logics for signals</li>

<li>Horia Corcalciuc, graduated 2014. Thesis title:  Taxonomies for software security</li>

</ul>



